This paper proposes a method for generating parallel corpus for any language pairs using video subtitles, which is related to natural language processing and machine translation (cs.CL). The method involves automated crawling and downloading of subtitles, which involves information retrieval techniques (cs.IR). The use of video subtitles also involves multimedia processing (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks for complex translators, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
